itle\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.545596584884097e-26, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}, {\"begin\": 990, \"end\": 1001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.87244600067325e-21, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Wala po kaming pagsidlan ng tuwa para kay Carlos Edriel Yulo sa kanyang pambihirang tagumpay sa pagkamit ang dalawang gintong medalya sa Paris Olympics 2024(We can not contain our happiness for Carlos Edriel Yulo for achieving an outstanding victory of winning two gold medals at the Paris Olympics 2024),\\\" Lacuna said.\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1464, \"end\": 1482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Edriel Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"By achieving this incredible feat, Carlos Yulo has forever etched his name in the annals of Philippine and Asian sports,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1627, \"end\": 1638, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}, {\"begin\": 1699, \"end\": 1704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.4158466630438686e-13, \"text\