\"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The city government also plans to coordinate with the Department of Education and private schools in Manila so students can witness the parade.\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2264, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2222, \"end\": 2228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\", \"score\": 0.9999999997000941, \"rank\": 2.998956373615555e-10, \"text\": \"Manila\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This way, what they only see on TV, they can experience up close,\\\" Lacuna said.\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2346, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Caloy's victory will serve as an inspiration for them to discover more Carlos Yulos among the youth of Manila and the entire Philippines.\\\"\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2451, \"end\": 2457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\", \"score\": 0.9999999997000941, \"rank\": 2.998956373615555e-10, \"text\": \"Manila\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\"}, {\"begin\": 2473, \"end\": 2484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.87244600067325e-21, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yulo was born and raised in the capital city.\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2533, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He grew up in Leveriza St, a stone's throw from the Rizal Memorial Sports Complex (RMSC).\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2624, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At seven years old, after being discovered tumbling at a playground, Yulo was brought by his grandfather to the Gymnastics Association of the Philippines inside th